<document>
  <header>
    <title>POSTNET</title>
  </header>
  <body>
    <section id="example">
      <title>Example</title>
      <figure src="../images/example-postnet.png" alt="Example POSTNET symbol"/>
    </section>
    <section id="structure">
      <title>Structure</title>
      <p>The configuration for the default implementation is:</p>
      <source>&#60;barcode&#62;
  &#60;<strong>postnet</strong>&#62;
      &#60;height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:15mm}&#60;/height&#62;
      &#60;module-width&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.02in}&#60;/module-width&#62;
      &#60;quiet-zone enabled="{<link href="barcode-xml.html#boolean">boolean</link>:true}"&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:10mw}&#60;/quiet-zone&#62;
      &#60;checksum&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#checksum-mode">checksum-mode</link>:auto=ignore}&#60;/checksum&#62;
      &#60;interchar-gap-width&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.026in}&#60;/interchar-gap-width&#62;
      &#60;tall-bar-height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.125in}&#60;/tall-bar-height&#62;
      &#60;short-bar-height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.050in}&#60;/short-bar-height&#62;
      &#60;baseline-alignment&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#baseline-alignment">baseline-alignment</link>:bottom}&#60;/baseline-alignment&#62;
      &#60;human-readable&#62;
        &#60;placement&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#human-readable-placement">human-readable-placement</link>:none}&#60;/placement&#62;
        &#60;font-name&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#font-name">font-name</link>:Helvetica}&#60;/font-name&#62;
        &#60;font-size&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:8pt}&#60;/font-size&#62;
        &#60;display-checksum&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#boolean">boolean</link>:false}&#60;/display-checksum&#62;
      &#60;/human-readable&#62;
  &#60;/<strong>postnet</strong>&#62;
&#60;/barcode&#62;</source>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Message format</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Valid characters are 0-9</li>
        <li>display-checksum controls whether the calculated checksum should be included in the human-readable part.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>

